#: ../../source/examples/inverse.rst:77 6a51a07790a2459db85a273cb8893d71
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\min_{\\rho} \\quad C(\\rho) = \\mathbf{u}^T \\mathbf{K}(\\rho) "
